dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Outagamie County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2020 and includes the layers 'Outagamie_Roads_2020' and 'Outagamie_ROW_2020'.ROW: [Included is a polygon feature class representing the right of way boundaries within Outagamie County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
